Presenting a new Stand Up Comedy series 
Unrealistic Bollywood Movies Ft. Dil Chahta Hai.

Hope you enjoy this video. 

And Yes, After a wild tour of Kaafi Wild Hai, I am presenting my new show 
GENUINELY which I am touring these days. 
Why Genuinely? Because this time everything from heart so everything is Genuine.

Aao show mien, sab content GENUINE milega.

en.title: Gautam Adani vs Hindenburg Report | Explained by Dhruv Rathee
en.description:
A few days back, Hindenburg released a report on Adani Group alleging that the group is involved in stock manipulation and accounting fraud, which not only led to Adani's big loss but also a huge deviation in the stock market. Farq Episode 29 - [Eng Sub] - Faysal Quraishi - Sehar Khan - Adeel Chaudhry - 6th February 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Farq is the story of two different individuals, Irsa (Sehar Khan) and Kamal (Faysal Quraishi) who come together to form an unusual union under compromising circumstances. 
From the outside, Irsa and Kamal seem not to be made for each other. They are too different in terms of character, life choices, desires and socio-economic background. 
On one hand, Irsa desires to live a life of luxury while Kamal is fed up with the loneliness that his house offers. Despite being together as a couple, 
will the two ever look at the truth in themselves to determine who they are and what they want in life?

Written By: Imran Nazir
Directed By: Aehsun Talish
Produced By: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Recently cbse has changed the style of English Question paper where Unseen passage has also seen some significant changes .The new pattern focuses on analysing student's competency that has made this topic a little complicated. Thapki ‡§®‡•á ‡§¨‡§§‡§æ‡§Ø‡§æ Tina-Bani ‡§ï‡•ã ‡§Ö‡§™‡§®‡§æ ‡§Ö‡§§‡•Ä‡§§ | Thapki Pyar Ki | ‡§•‡§™‡§ï‡•Ä ‡§™‡•ç‡§Ø‡§æ‡§∞ ‡§ï‡•Ä | Full Episode | Ep. 616

After eavesdropping on Shraddha's conversation with Sankar, Thapki finds out that Tina is her own daughter. Thapki then discloses the details of her past to Bani and Tina. What will be Thapki's next move to get Bihaan's memory back?

The bright and beautiful Thapki is pretty much perfect... except for one minor flaw - she stammers. But that doesn't hold her back. All she needs is an encouraging pat on the back,a 'thapki', which soon becomes her name. Over the course of the show, Thapki falls in love with Dhruv, but is duped into getting married to his brother, Bihaan. In spite of this cruel twist of fate, Thapki doesn't let her spirit fade and does all she can to be the ideal bahu. What does destiny hold for this charming girl with an unbeatable spirit?

Roohe nee akalum munbuppane kandu marikkenam.
Allekil ummantte koode marikkenam.
Roohe nee piriyum munbuppane kandu marikkenam.
Vidhiyundel uppantte koode madagenam.
Ee mannil thunanigal pakaliravil punjagal...
Cheru novum ariyunnor.
Nira sneham pakarunnor.
Vanathil keezhe eni ennennum thudarenam...
     (Roohe..)

Thalarathe thakarathe duniyavil thanalayi ee ummantte nizhalayi ennum njanille.
Cherukudilil padavukalil mizhi edarathoru thiriyayi enn varavennum kaakkanoru nizhalayi neeyille.
Niramazhayil eriveyilil oru kudayay njanille.
Oru karuthal kadalakan ennuppa koottunde.
Niraravil nilav pozhinjath poloru sneham pakarunne.
Kalichiriyil kadha parayan  ennumma koodunde.
Kadhanathil karamekan ennuppa koottunde.
     (Roohe...)

Kaalathin oolethil ozhukunne cheruvanchi.
Athinerathii snehathin thuzhayayi njanunde.
Oru kattil ulayathe oru thirayil thakarathe ee janmathil kadavil thunayakanivanundo.
Oru theeyayi anayunnor ee maanava janmagal.
Oru theeyum pozhiyathe pakarami snehagal.
Udayorith ummayuppayum ulakiluyiril swasagal.
Oru puzhathan thelineeram ee sneham pakaramo.
Oru kadalin alapole ee sneham pakaramo.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3687 - 6 Feb 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3687: Jhoot Ka Jaal
--------------------------------------------------------
Bapuji shares his story about how he escaped with everybody at Gokuldham. He never went to the park, and that is why Jetha and Sodhi never found him there; instead, he was at the clubhouse. When Champaklal was heading towards the park, he came across Tapu Sena and decided to play tennis at the clubhouse. When Tapu Sena and Champaklal saw Taarak's boss from the balcony, they immediately hid him. Champaklal tore off the head of the brand-new floor mop, which Abdul bought and wore as a hair wig. Everyone at Gokuldham was impressed by Champaklal's impromptu idea. Stay tuned to learn more!

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3687, 6 Feb 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Josh Talks passionately believes that a well-told story has the power to reshape attitudes, lives, and ultimately, the world. We are on a mission to find and showcase the best motivational stories from across India through documented videos and live events held all over the country. Josh Talks Malayalam caters to the Malayalam-speaking audience worldwide. It aims to inspire and motivate Malayalees by showcasing Malayalam motivation through the experiences of fellow Malayalis. Josh talks Malayalam and brings to you the best Malayalam motivational videos. What started as a simple conference is now a fast-growing media platform that covers the most innovative rags to riches success stories with speakers from every conceivable background, including entrepreneurship, women‚Äôs rights, public policy, sports, entertainment, and social initiatives. snippet.description:
Anjali wants to buy a bungalow worth 30 crores. She comes with Rahul to deal with that bungalow but Rahul refuses to buy it saying that it is very expensive. This makes Anjali sad. The next day, the news of Rahul's car being burnt comes in the news. CID reaches the crime scene to investigate the case. Who is behind this incident with Rahul? Watch the full episode to know how team CID will solve this mysterious case.

Show Name: CID 
Show Cast & Characters: 
‚Ä¢ Shivaji Satam as ACP Praduman
‚Ä¢ Dinesh Phadnis as Inspector Fredricks aka Freddy

#CID #livcrime #‡§∏‡•Ä‡§Ü‡§à‡§°‡•Ä #cid2023 #newcid #crime #latestcid

About CID:
-----------------
The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam]. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 3687 - Champak Chacha Saves The Day?! | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | ‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï ‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada

Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer

snippet.title: Second earthquake hits in Turkey after more than 1,000 killed - BBC News
snippet.description:
Another large earthquake has hit south-eastern Turkey, after a first 7.8-magnitude tremor killed more than 900 people in the country and hundreds more in Syria.¬†

Rescuers are racing to save people trapped beneath the rubble after hundreds of buildings collapsed in both countries.¬†

World leaders have pledged to send aid after Turkey issued an international appeal for help.¬†

Please subscribe here.¬†

#Turkey #Syria #BBCNews
